caption.text: You can't have your feet in everything and expect to win. It's about being realistic most of the time. Stop saying yes to everyone. When you run in many directions, you end up with far less than you expected! You win where you can give the most value at, so focus there first.

caption.text: Talent? You're bummed out you don't have enought TALENT? Wait, HARD WORK isn't talent.. FOCUS isn't talent.. OPTIMISM isn't talent.. PATIENCE isn't talent.. GRATITUDE isn't talent.. SELF AWARENESS isn't talent! Don't kid yourself and keep making excuses for not winning at what you're good at, you're better than that!

caption.text: Do you see people treating the weekdays like a weekend? Greatttt! The more people around who work like that, the more piece of the pie left for you! Get fired up about putting in the work when you have to and getting one step ahead of everybody else while they rest on the sidelines! Hustle while they don't, win when they won't!

#stepup #stepout #soar Don't be so passive! If you want something amazing to happen you can't juz wait for someone to give it to you! Step up and take the wheel, don't just sit under a rock! Step out of your comfort zone, do things differently from now on so you dont get back to those same old results. Soar through the noise, there's bound to be a lot of friction the more you hustle, people won't have the the same mindset as you, dont expect them to!! #entrepreneurship
#dreams #regret #do Thousands of us can dream but only a few of us take action! You get to choose whether you're just a dreamer or a doer or both and decide at 105 how much regret you can take!

#finishit #dontdelay #decide #takeaction Do you have many overlooked, overdue, unfinished business, that puts a ton of weight in the back of your head that you don't need?! Either you decide to forget it forever or you do something to get it off your back!  It can be demanding, uncomfortable, time consuming, but stop complaining! You decide if it is something important or not, if it is, go out there and figure out how to finish it so it doesn't finish you. Finish the unfinished!

#HappyNewYear #2017 Please, don't wait until you feel sick of hiding behind what others expect of you. Don't waste a year of worrying what other people might think of you. Don't let another 365 days go by without you at least trying to be the real you. Don't finish 2017 and never have tried your best to do what you love! This is your moment and if you only live once, how would you live it with the least regret? Happy New Years my friends! live with pasdion, patience, and intent!

caption.text: #resolutions2017 #resolutions #2017 However you wanna play this, there's nothing worse than scheduling yourself in the future to start something significant that you can be starting now and after that spend time beating up yourself for not stepping up on your promise to only do it all over again next year. Can't think of a better time to start than now nor a worse time to want to begin than later! If it's so important, dont wait for a resolution to take action!

#grounded #achieve #journey Never forget, whatever it is your soo busy doing right now can become soo insignificant tomorrow when someone you care so much about is gone, forever! Not wishing bad things to anyone here, but we need to be grateful for what we have, less judgemental of our misfortunes, and more respectful of our tiny achievements, coz the more grounded you are, the more you realize your climb is not only more significant than reaching the top, but it's also the determining factor to even get there!

#selfawareness You don't get a chance to be like someone else, to be like Zuckerberg or Kobe, in fact you were out here to dominate by being what you're uniquely good at, you have the opportunity to use you're one life to wake up and crush it your way. Stop wasting time doing what you think would be nice to do, do things that you know you can't breathe without. FIND YOUR OXYGEN!
